Description


Additional information


Reviews (0)




Johnathan Kayne Judith nude is a simple open toe sandal.  The 3 3/4 inch heel will give you great height at your occasion.  The nude color is awesome because it matches both cool colors and warm colors, in addition to black and white.  There is a single thin strap that crosses the front of the foot giving more support.  Judith has a closed back to keep your heel in place, and it also has an adjustable ankle strap to ensure optimal support.  There is a gold clasp on the adjustable ankle strap adding a modern sense to this fashionable shoe.




